{"type": "article", "id": 12554, "title": "云朵卫生纸托盘", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-24T08:08:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135744e8XYRkvc4CwB6Dhu.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t法国设计师 Bertrand Jayr 和 Lyon Béton 推出了一款卫生纸托盘，托盘呈云彩的形状，当一卷卷的纸巾放在上面后，看起来更像是一朵可爱的云彩。托盘固定在墙上，氛围大小号两种，可以根据卫生间的大小进行选择。<a href=\"http://us.lyon-beton.com/shop/cloud-s-toilet-paper-shelf/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140248X2qgR4HfipI7BcDY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140248qApITQCXPolOL8tM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140249TqQGyPsRen3Cwl0o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140249KB2ao5PcjUXqTdSG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}